        "description": "Beam diameter range for cleaning; smaller for fine details (100-200 μm), larger for broad areas (300-500 μm). Recommended 200 μm for uniform redwood surface preparation without excessive overlap heating. Source: Equipment specifications from Coherent and Trumpf laser cleaners for industrial wood applications."
